#request-form.contact-form
    h3.title.contact-form__title Get a free consultation 
    form
        .contact-form__fields 
            .contact-form__field
                .contact-form__label
                    input(type="text" placeholder="Fist name" aria-label="First name").field.contact-form__input
                    svg(height="14" width="14").icon.contact-form__icon
                        use(href="./assets/images/icons.svg#user")

            .contact-form__field
                .contact-form__label
                    button(type="button").button.contact-form__flag-btn 
                        img(height="12" width="24" src="./assets/images/flag.png" alt="flag").contact-form__flag-image
                        svg(height="6" width="9").icon.contact-form__select-icon 
                            use(href="./assets/images/icons.svg#down-arrow")
                    input(type="tel" value="+ 971 123 4567" aria-label="Telephone number").field.contact-form__input.contact-form__tel
                    svg(height="14" width="14").icon.contact-form__icon
                        use(href="./assets/images/icons.svg#phone")

            .contact-form__field
                .contact-form__label
                    input(type="text" placeholder="Email adress" aria-label="Email adress").field.contact-form__input
                    svg(height="14" width="14").icon.contact-form__icon
                        use(href="./assets/images/icons.svg#mail")

        .contact-form__submit-wrapper 
            button(type="submit").button.contact-form__submit Get a consultation
            p.contact-form__accepting-text 
                | By clicking the button you are accepting to receive an email about club membership and a phone call to arrange a show-around.
